Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.43,0:17:32.83,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fax-0.15}{\pos(352,510)}不知何时也受人摆布
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.83,0:17:35.17,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fax-0.15}{\pos(352,510)}如果讨厌的话   就把那墙壁
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.17,0:17:37.90,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fax-0.15}{\pos(352,510)}{\fad(0,500)}现在马上敲碎 !!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.00,0:17:40.24,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fax-0.15}{\pos(352,510)}对你来说
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.24,0:17:42.71,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fax-0.15}{\pos(352,510)}纵使我的世界被黑暗所吞噬
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.71,0:17:45.01,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fax-0.15}{\pos(352,510)}想为你带来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.01,0:17:47.44,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fax-0.15}{\pos(352,510)}满是爱的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.44,0:17:49.45,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fax-0.15}{\pos(352,510)}那硕大的梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.45,0:17:50.65,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fax-0.15}{\pos(352,510)}就此出发去寻找
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.65,0:17:52.72,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fax-0.15}{\pos(352,510)}虽然看不见    但确实
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.72,0:17:55.05,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fax-0.15}{\pos(352,510)}{\fad(0,500)}那声音
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.15,0:17:59.42,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fax-0.15}{\pos(352,510)\fad(0,700)}就此倾听吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:34:28.40,0:34:30.64,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fax-0.15}{\pos(352,510)}那硕大的梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:34:30.64,0:34:33.04,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fax-0.15}{\pos(352,510)}就此出发去寻找
Dialogue: 0,0:34:33.04,0:34:35.44,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fax-0.15}{\pos(352,510)}满是罪孽的
Dialogue: 0,0:34:35.44,0:34:37.91,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fax-0.15}{\pos(352,510)}每天的爱
Dialogue: 0,0:34:37.91,0:34:38.61,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fax-0.15}{\pos(352,510)}请给予我
